    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a set of extensions to the Certificate Management over CMS (CMC) protocol that addresses the desire to support server-side generation of keys. This service is provided by the definition of additional control statements within the CMC architecture. Additional CMC errors are also defined.</t>
